'''列俄帕尔格阿勒峰'''（Reo Purgyil; Leo Pargial, Leo Pargil<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://web.utk.edu/~mjessup/Jessup/Leo_Pargil_dome.html |title=Leo Pargil dome |accessdate=2015-10-25 |archive-date=2016-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161021171505/http://web.utk.edu/~mjessup/Jessup/Leo_Pargil_dome.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>），中国与印度的界山[[普日山|普日山]]（[[拉克马山|拉克马山]]；Lakhma）的最高峰，位于中国西藏[[阿里地区|阿里地区]][[札达县|札达县]]西北及印度[[喜马偕尔邦|喜马偕尔邦]][[拉豪爾和斯皮提縣|拉豪爾和斯皮提縣]]地区的边界线上，[[什布奇山口|什布奇山口]]北侧14 km，海拔6816m，地理坐标为{{coord|31|53|03|N|78|44|08|E}}，印度人称之为“魔鬼岩”<ref name="himalayanclub">{{cite news|author=E. THEOPHILUS|title=REO PURGYIL — BENEATH THE SHROUD|url=http://www.himalayanclub.org/journal/reo-purgyil-%E2%80%94-beneath-the-shroud/|website=himalayanclub|date=1990–1991|accessdate=2013-06-21|archive-date=2017-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170206185123/https://www.himalayanclub.org/journal/reo-purgyil-%e2%80%94-beneath-the-shroud/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。离此峰不远的中国札达县境内，有座藏传佛教的古寺[[普日寺|普日寺]](Puri Gompa)。

